OL,6,FPolice in Glasgow held children in
OL,7,Fcustody for too long with no record of
OL,8,Ftheir reason for doing so, inspectors
OL,9,Ffound.
OL,11,FHM Inspectorate of Constabulary in
OL,12,FScotland (HMICS) and Healthcare
OL,13,FImprovement Scotland reviewed custody
OL,14,Fcentres at London Road, Govan and
OL,15,FCathcart police stations in September
OL,16,F2024.
