OL,3,CSeveral children detained in police
OL,4,Ccustody for too long, inspectors find
OL,6,FInspectors examined a sample of 90
OL,7,Fcustody records from July 2024 which
OL,8,Frevealed five occasions when children
OL,9,Faged between 13 and 17 were held in
OL,10,Fcells for longer than they deemed
OL,11,Fnecessary.
OL,13,FA 13-year-old was held in custody for
OL,14,Fmore than six hours, three children
OL,15,Faged 14 were held for more than six,
OL,16,F10 and 12 hours respectively, and a 16-
OL,17,Fyear-old was held overnight for more
OL,18,Fthan nine hours, the inspectors found.
