OL,3,CSeveral children detained in police
OL,4,Ccustody for too long, inspectors find
OL,6,FThe HMICS report said on each occasion
OL,7,Fthe youngsters ` none of whom were
OL,8,Fbeing held for court appearances ` had
OL,9,Fbeen charged with what they considered
OL,10,Fto be "minor offences".
OL,12,FThe report also noted there was no
OL,13,Frecord on the Police Scotland National
OL,14,FCustody System to indicate a custody
OL,15,Finspector was aware of, or had
OL,16,Fsanctioned, the detention decisions.
