OL,3,CSeveral children detained in police
OL,4,Ccustody for too long, inspectors find
OL,6,FInspectors said the provision of
OL,7,Fhealthcare within each of the custody
OL,8,Fcentres was good but noted custody
OL,9,Fstaff and local policing officers had
OL,10,Fdescribed staffing shortages as "very
OL,11,Fchallenging".
OL,13,FThe HMICS report recommended Police
OL,14,FScotland examine staffing levels at
OL,15,Fthe custody centres and make
OL,16,Farrangements to ensure appropriate
OL,17,Fstaffing levels are in place.
OL,19,FIt also highlighted concerns regarding
OL,20,Fa lack of consistency in the recording
OL,21,Fof information.
