OL,6,FMr Naylor said: "We have continued to
OL,7,Ffind disparities, in some cases,
OL,8,Fbetween the risk assessments
OL,9,Fundertaken and the corresponding care
OL,10,Fplans put in place to mitigate risk.
OL,12,F"Similarly, we found a lack of quality
OL,13,Fassurance of operational practice
OL,14,Ftaking place ` an issue which we have
OL,15,Fraised previously and have made a
OL,16,Frecommendation for improvement.
