OL,3,CSeveral children detained in police
OL,4,Ccustody for too long, inspectors find
OL,6,F"While recommendations outlined in
OL,7,Fthis report have specific relevance
OL,8,Ffor Glasgow custody centres, some will
OL,9,Fbe equally applicable to other custody
OL,10,Fcentres across Scotland and should be
OL,11,Fconsidered in future improvement
OL,12,Fplanning by Police Scotland's criminal
OL,13,Fjustice services division."
OL,15,FPolice Scotland Assistant Chief
OL,16,FConstable Wendy Middleton said the
OL,17,Fforce welcomes the report and will
OL,18,F"carefully consider" the findings and
OL,19,Frecommendations.
