OL,6,F"We have made it clear that police
OL,7,Fcustody is no place for children and
OL,8,Fyoung people, and we are actively
OL,9,Fworking with stakeholders including
OL,10,Fthe Children's Commissioner to explore
OL,11,Fappropriate alternatives to police
OL,12,Fcustody for children and young people
OL,13,Fand to minimise the occasions on which
OL,14,Fit may be necessary."
